('Pothole On Road', true, 'Thanks for reporting this pothole. We''ve filed this request with RVA311 on your behalf. Pothole requests are inspected and repaired within 14 days, weather permitting. If this is a duplicate request, if no pothole can be found, or extended paving is needed, timelines could be extended.'),
