('Vehicle Personal Property Taxes', false, 'Requests related to Vehicle Personal Property taxes should be submitted through the Department of Finance''s new RVA Pay system. Please use the RVAPay link to access the new system and register for an account. In RVAPay you will be able to see all outstanding bills, view all of your past bills and make payments: rvapay.rva.gov'),
('How To Report Mosquitoes On Public Property', false, 'Mosquito concerns are assessed and addressed by different departments within the city depending on their origin. Go to RVA311.com to find links to the appropriate forms.'),
