('How To Request Police Attendance At Community Event', false, 'To request police presence at an event, Contact the Sector Lieutenant for the Sector where the event will be held to arrange scheduling. To verify the correct sector and appropriate contact information, visit the Richmond Police Patrol Services page: https://www.rva.gov/police/patrol-services'),
